# Enny Mtshweni — Developer Portfolio

A personal developer portfolio built as part of the fswd deleverables .

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Custom Properties, Flexbox, Grid)
- Bootstrap 5
- JavaScript (vanilla ES6+)

## Features
- Responsive design (mobile-first)
- Animated typewriter hero text
- Scroll-triggered card reveal
- Active navbar link tracking
- Project cards with hover overlay
- Contact form with validation and feedback
- Accessible (skip link, ARIA labels, keyboard-navigable)
- Dark theme with amber accent

## Sections
1. Hero
2. About
3. Skills
4. Projects
5. Contact

